{"type":"message","id":"cb6a49d1","parentId":"4841772a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T04:19:13.060Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to SSH into the new VPS and set up OpenClaw for them. Key points:\n1. SSH into the new VPS\n2. Install and configure OpenClaw\n3. Use ONE shared bot token for all agents (not separate bot per agent)\n4. No groups, just direct messages (no group config)\n5. Replace all tokens/API keys\n\nBut I need the VPS IP and credentials first. Let me ask for them.","thinkingSignature":"ed8bddeeea8a208d4d13f10eeecd4ba9db9e3156f37771bce2849edd28f54b88"},{"type":"text","text":"Cần thông tin đăng nhập VPS mới:\n\n1. **IP VPS:** ?\n2. **Username/password hoặc SSH key:** ?\n\nSau khi có, tôi sẽ SSH vào và setup toàn bộ. Lưu ý:\n- **1 bot token duy nhất** cho tất cả agents (dùng chung `dmPolicy: \"pairing\"`)\n- Không có group config\n- Các API key (AHV, GitLab, Figma, Stitch, Google) — tôi dùng token hiện tại hay bạn cung cấp token mới?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":229,"output":242,"cacheRead":25629,"cacheWrite":10650,"totalTokens":36750,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776745136834,"responseId":"06362db2a7d02cc231e58bfea73850b0"}}
