{"type":"message","id":"0e0d6b43","parentId":"30c06779","timestamp":"2026-04-21T04:29:29.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, only one gateway is running now. But wait - the new gateway (PID 339020) was started with the environment variables I passed, but the openclaw.json on the VPS uses env variable placeholders like `${TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN}`. The VPS might not have these env vars set in a persistent way (e.g., in bashrc or systemd service).\n\nLet me check if the gateway is using the new openclaw.json config. Also, I should set up the env vars persistently in bashrc or as a systemd service.\n\nLet me also check if there's a way to set env vars in openclaw itself, or if I should add them to /root/.bashrc.","thinkingSignature":"375541252bb8c3974f14307c7b09d9c6196e6d41bc1574f85cc8ead4e9d66089"},{"type":"text","text":"Giờ set env vars bền vững trong bashrc:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_28qa3utgkk0r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sshpass -p '0zDxl1N36E(p@J' ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no root@161.248.81.138 'cat >> /root/.bashrc << '\\''EOF'\\''\nexport PNPM_HOME=\"/root/.local/share/pnpm\"\nexport PATH=\"$PNPM_HOME:$PATH\"\nexport AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=\"sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-w85g8t-b82baf0b\"\nexport GITLAB_TOKEN=\"glpat-rjgwaQjEp7hL_skbf8lXamM6MQpvOjEKdTpsNWJ5Zw8.01.171o9yg1e\"\nexport TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=\"8605080868:AAFFvDZs3YwWfxaLgW7Lgj42ANwyFIzmFT8\"\nexport STITCH_API_KEY=\"AQ.Ab8RN6KimOxDQ4kNCgR68MBTO9qonEhjKMoCfu744Y4dWUblAg\"\nexport CONFLUENCE_URL=\"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/wiki\"\nexport CONFLUENCE_EMAIL=\"dqcuong.work@gmail.com\"\nexport CONFLUENCE_TOKEN=\"ATATT3xFfGF03z7i01Hgl_4UzecsdxxBKCs10EFmrVwCmT1zeLPRxhkOKMv5eIqgKbTWPdTISeYkx7YdcdBkDy9_sduO2Rlu95A6XHfnFL3efXUCqva3JyFNVFAoFIYGqSX_Jvw4oc7JOaVVEjfpZhRd3DebLI_93JjEOGcliM_alSWdh01RY9c=44ED3599\"\nEOF\necho \"Env vars added to bashrc\"'","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":