{"type":"message","id":"241c0822","parentId":"3968c6c3","timestamp":"2026-04-21T04:55:47.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a systemd service `openclaw-gateway.service` that's running! That's why the gateway keeps restarting - it's managed by systemd. I need to update the systemd service or the openclaw.json that systemd is using.\n\nLet me check the systemd service configuration.","thinkingSignature":"00d213cd2d93e3d7f89b02e1860849b0a2558c9899282bfda1b675f8b0239335"},{"type":"text","text":"**Found it!** Có systemd service đang quản lý gateway. Kiểm tra service config:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ju2kq0o7g9do_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sshpass -p '0zDxl1N36E(p@J' ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no root@161.248.81.138 'cat /etc/systemd/system/openclaw-gateway.service'","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":107,"output":156,"cacheRead":92990,"cacheWrite":853,"totalTokens":94106,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776747341944,"responseId":"0636364fde9203ad3bc32a5e2b5ec131"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d295f9a","parentId":"241c0822","timestamp":"2026-04-21T04:55:47.986Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ju2kq0o7g9do_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Gateway\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=root\nWorkingDirectory=/root/.openclaw\nEnvironment=\"AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-w85g8t-b82baf0b\"\nEnvironment=\"PATH=/usr/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin\"\nExecStart=/usr/bin/openclaw gateway --port 18789\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=10\nStandardOutput=journal\nStandardError=journal\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":759,"aggregated":"[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Gateway\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=root\nWorkingDirectory=/root/.openclaw\nEnvironment=\"AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-w85g8t-b82baf0b\"\nEnvironment=\"PATH=/usr/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin\"\nExecStart=/usr/bin/openclaw gateway --port 18789\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=10\nStandardOutput=journal\nStandardError=journal\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776747347975}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc13dee4","parentId":"0d295f9a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T04:55:59.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the issue. The systemd service is using a simplified startup command: `/usr/bin/openclaw gateway --port 18789`. It's only passing `--port 18789` and not loading the full openclaw.json config with all the env vars properly.\n\nAlso, the service doesn't have all the env vars I set. It only has `AHVHOLDING_API_KEY`. I need to update the systemd service to include all the env vars.\n\nBut actually, the service is loading the config from `/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json` (via `WorkingDirectory=/root/.openclaw`). So the config should be picked up. But the issue is that:\n\n\nThe gateway binary might be loading a cached or default config instead of the one in the working directory, and it could be running with different parameters than expected. Let me check the Telegram bot status first—if it's connected, the core functionality is working and I can focus on getting the API port 18789 accessible, which might just be a matter of exposing it through the gateway configuration.\n\nActually, the simpler path forward is to update the systemd service with all the necessary environment variables and restart it.","thinkingSignature":"55f9d636d07075edc9ed72b53e6b1d2f91a31dbca9141eb3d3c3d369ce55d90d"},{"type":"text","text":"Systemd service thiếu các env vars. Cập nhật service config:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1fdhjm93izxe_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sshpass -p '0zDxl1N36E(p@J' ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no root@161.248.81.138 'cat > /etc/systemd/system/openclaw-gateway.service << '\\''EOF'\\''\n[Unit]\nDescription=OpenClaw Gateway\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=root\nWorkingDirectory=/root/.openclaw\nEnvironment=\"AHVHOLDING_API_KEY=sk-3d8edc47e4037bc4-w85g8t-b82baf0b\"\nEnvironment=\"GITLAB_TOKEN=glpat-rjgwaQjEp7hL_skbf8lXamM6MQpvOjEKdTpsNWJ5Zw8.01.171o9yg1