{"type":"message","id":"7103617c","parentId":"596bf7ce","timestamp":"2026-04-21T04:57:38.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway is responding with HTTP 200! It's serving the web UI. Let me now verify the Telegram bot is working by checking the Telegram API.\n\nNow let me summarize what has been set up and what still needs to be done.The setup is mostly complete:\n1. ✅ OpenClaw installed (v2026.4.15 via npm)\n2. ✅ openclaw.json uploaded with all 38 agents, single Telegram bot, new API keys\n3. ✅ Skills copied (38 skills)\n4. ✅ Agents copied (38 agents + workspaces)\n\n\n5. ✅ Gateway running and listening on 127.0.0.1:18789\n6. ✅ Systemd service configured with all env vars\n7. ✅ Telegram bot connected (verified earlier via API)\n\nThe bot is working—it's connected to Telegram and responding to messages. The only thing left to handle is exposing the gateway port from loopback if remote access is needed, but that's optional. I should update the memory with the new VPS IP and wrap this up for the user.","thinkingSignature":"750f103c73ae258c93e893583c455a38eab244d8e9630194c640e158a6ad663f"},{"type":"text","text":"**Gateway đang chạy và respond!** 🎉\n\nTóm tắt setup hoàn tất trên VPS **161.248.81.138**:\n\n✅ **Đã setup:**\n- OpenClaw 2026.4.15 (npm)\n- 38 agents + 38 skills\n- 1 Telegram bot (`@tieuvydev_bot`)\n- Tất cả API keys (AHV, GitLab, Figma, Stitch, Confluence)\n- Gateway listening on `127.0.0.1:18789`\n- Systemd service auto-start\n\n⚠️ **Lưu ý:** Gateway port 18789 chỉ binding loopback (`127.0.0.1`). Muốn truy cập từ bên ngoài cần đổi `bind: \"loopback\"` → `\"bind: \"0.0.0.0\"` trong config.\n\nBạn đã có thể nhắn tin cho `@tieuvydev_bot` trên Telegram để test!"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":408,"output":441,"cacheRead":98039,"cacheWrite":206,"totalTokens":99094,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"st